Template: opsi/configure_samba
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Edit samba config?
 It is possible to add the needed samba shares and users
 but if your samba config get messed up you have been warned!

Template: opsi/configure_dhcpd
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Edit dhcpd config?
 It is possible to add the needed options to your dhcp server config
 but if your config get messed up you have been warned!

Template: opsi/configure_sudoers
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Edit sudoers config?
 It is possible add the needed options to your sudoers file
 but if your config get messed up you have been warned!

